{"tid":1054510,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)綠箭俠 第1-2季","createTime":"2019-03-10T00:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T08:35:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"00daa50094ad9d3b94be2923327ce3096480da3e","tid":1054510,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:15:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=50bb485d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=c68405c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=abbf1e59\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.diziizle.es/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/arrow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.diziizle.es%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Farrow.png&h=ee748f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一季<br />\n<br />\n    故事敘述昆氏企業總裁之子奧利佛．奎恩原本是位玩世不恭的花花公子，後來獨自在海難中存活下來。他在孤島上生存了五年，回國後為了完成父親的遺願，而變裝成「綠箭俠」在斯塔林市（Starling City）打擊犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n第二季<br />\n好友死後的Oliver沉寂了許久，之後發現因莎朵(Shado)之死而痛恨Oliver的斯萊德威爾森(Slade Wilson),來到了星城,並誓言摧毀Oliver所珍視的一切。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=b56a0551\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2PFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=03537fec\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031547a54546415a9888c1552b197534c331a719","tid":1054510,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1b77924b24f61cbcae7104a4aa3382715eb1cb","tid":1054510,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32deaac77b37b803a04c7ba70096c85a52c9be0","tid":1054510,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c724e63fc5a7352ae65841801d49cf6a7e6bae","tid":1054510,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re